<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">步步惊心：丽</span>角色介绍</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="4" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="juesejieshao" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="lemmaWgt-roleIntroduction">
<ul>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%83%8A%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BD/19226575/0/10dfa9ec8a136327b628b8b3998fa0ec09fac76d?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/-4o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D0%2C0%2C652%2C927%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=6077c3e49ceef01f595b4285ddceb515/10dfa9ec8a136327b628b8b3998fa0ec09fac76d.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%8E%8B%E6%98%AD/19850055" data-lemmaid="19850055">王昭</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9D%8E%E5%87%86%E5%9F%BA">李准基</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
<span class="item-key">配音</span>
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BA%8E%E6%AD%A3%E6%98%8C">于正昌</a>
；<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%BD%97%E4%BC%9F%E6%9D%B0">罗伟杰</a>
</span>
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
四王子，王后刘氏为独占丈夫的爱，将幼子王昭作为人质威胁丈夫，意外在昭脸上留下伤疤，事后将他送给庆州姜氏做养子。在“看脸”的高丽时代，王昭被迫戴着面具，成为面目可怖的“狼狗”。除夕傩礼仪式，昭再次见到母亲，面对他的仍是偏见和冷遇，但看着对他说“不要因为伤疤，毁了整个人生”的解树，王昭开始了不同的人生。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%83%8A%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BD/19226575/0/a044ad345982b2b7c7a65c4439adcbef76099b70?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D0%2C14%2C652%2C927%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=8f2622be04f3d7ca18b96536cf2f9238/a044ad345982b2b7c7a65c4439adcbef76099b70.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%A7%A3%E6%A0%91">解树</a>/高夏珍
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9D%8E%E7%9F%A5%E6%81%A9">李知恩</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
<span class="item-key">配音</span>
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9D%A8%E5%87%AF%E5%87%AF">杨凯凯</a>
；石梓晴
</span>
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
王旭妻子明伊的堂妹，为陪伴姐姐来到松岳，偷窥王子们沐浴时溺水昏迷。21世纪职员高夏珍遭遇恋人背叛后溺水，灵魂在解树体内醒来却苦寻不出回到现代的方法，她决定以解树的身份活下去。她与传统的高丽女子不同的语言行为，现代的思考方式，和特有的活泼气质，吸引了王子们的关注，也和王子们的命运、感情产生紧密的联系。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%83%8A%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BD/19226575/0/1b4c510fd9f9d72a9733759ddc2a2834359bbbdf?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D0%2C0%2C652%2C927%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=c72475af9dcad1c8c4f4a667420e4b39/1b4c510fd9f9d72a9733759ddc2a2834359bbbdf.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%8E%8B%E6%97%AD/19863743" data-lemmaid="19863743">王旭</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A7%9C%E6%B2%B3%E9%82%A3">姜河那</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
<span class="item-key">配音</span>
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%BB%84%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%91/5316219" data-lemmaid="5316219">黄天佑</a>
；<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%A2%81%E5%BE%B7%E5%9F%BA">袁德基</a>
</span>
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
八王子，文武双全，天生的领导者和政治家，善于收服人心为己用。与四王子王昭同年出生，但两人的命运、性格全然不同。被外婆皇甫家族全力推为王储，从未享受过属于自己的生活。突然出现的鬼丫头解树，给过着沉稳生活的旭带来欢笑和泪水。与政治联姻的夫人明伊相敬如宾，为了得到解树，必须在激烈的王位之争中取胜。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%83%8A%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BD/19226575/0/562c11dfa9ec8a13b15a3260ff03918fa1ecc0ea?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D0%2C0%2C652%2C927%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=21a3e43f845494ee936d555910c5ccce/562c11dfa9ec8a13b15a3260ff03918fa1ecc0ea.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%8E%8B%E5%B0%A7/19852906" data-lemmaid="19852906">王尧</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B4%AA%E5%AE%97%E7%8E%84">洪宗玄</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
<span class="item-key">配音</span>
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%94%A1%E5%BF%A0%E5%8D%AB">蔡忠卫</a>
；简怀甄（第15集接替）
</span>
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
三王子，王后刘氏一手打造的王储，外貌出众、家族势力强大、才能倶佳，他最大的遗憾是，因出生晚于大哥王武而未能成为太子，认为是王武抢夺了自己的位子。性格贪婪且傲慢，是兄弟们畏惧的对象。感情细腻，喜欢抓住弱点操纵他人，有洁癖，不喜欢自己手上沾血，后成为高丽第三代王“定宗”。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%83%8A%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BD/19226575/0/43a7d933c895d1433f5780a37bf082025aaf0708?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss2.bdstatic.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D0%2C27%2C652%2C927%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=f515988d78cf3bc7fc4f97acec309693/43a7d933c895d1433f5780a37bf082025aaf0708.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%8E%8B%E9%93%B6/20849629" data-lemmaid="20849629">王银</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%BE%B9%E4%BC%AF%E8%B4%A4">边伯贤</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
<span class="item-key">配音</span>
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BC%A0%E6%8C%AF%E7%86%99">张振熙</a>
</span>
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
十王子，开国功臣王规的外孙。天生爱玩，厌学厌武，一辈子“中二病”。血气方刚时，所有精力都放在“女人和恋爱”上。与解树相识后，对其产生初恋的感觉。随后被王赐婚，奉旨迎娶大将军朴守卿的女儿朴顺德。婚后也无法忘记解树的王银，一度让顺德伤心，但顺德一片痴心，慢慢让他产生了动摇。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%83%8A%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BD/19226575/0/d1a20cf431adcbef6dca1b86a4af2edda2cc9fb7?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/-Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D0%2C0%2C652%2C927%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=2218e64d5a66d0166a56c468aa1bf837/d1a20cf431adcbef6dca1b86a4af2edda2cc9fb7.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%8E%8B%E9%83%81/19863734" data-lemmaid="19863734">王郁</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%8D%97%E6%9F%B1%E8%B5%AB">南柱赫</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
<span class="item-key">配音</span>
<span class="item-value">
宋昱璁
；梁皓翔
</span>
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
十三王子，母亲为新罗亡国王室，继承王位无望，寄情于艺术，有很高的鉴赏能力，书画陶乐样样通，擅长玄鹤琴，兄弟们称其为“伯牙”。高丽第一美男，传闻他一出宫，全松岳的女人来不及穿鞋跑出围观。悠闲自得地享受人生，对国政有自己的见解。微服出访时偶遇虞姬并付出真心，但两人之间有无法克服的时代之痛。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item more">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%83%8A%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BD/19226575/0/77c6a7efce1b9d16c859fee1fbdeb48f8d546497?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/-vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D0%2C0%2C652%2C927%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=36ec2940ff36afc31a4365258e29c7f4/77c6a7efce1b9d16c859fee1fbdeb48f8d546497.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
王贞
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%87%91%E5%BF%97%E6%B4%99">金志洙</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
<span class="item-key">配音</span>
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%9D%9C%E6%99%AF%E7%85%9C">杜景煜</a>
</span>
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
十四王子，王尧、王昭同母所出，泡在蜜罐里长大的老幺。人见人爱，一旦陷入其魅力就无法自拔的如黑洞般的男人。但奇怪的是他的魅力对解树不管用，解树刚穿越到高丽时，他还是虚张声势的少年。数年战场历练归来后，成长为纯情漫画中让人怦然心动的男子汉。怀着对四王子王昭篡夺王位的疑心，誓要对抗到底。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item more">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%83%8A%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BD/19226575/0/b3fb43166d224f4affdb149301f790529922d1f4?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D0%2C0%2C652%2C927%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=962b5b93d554564ef12abe798eeeb0b2/b3fb43166d224f4affdb149301f790529922d1f4.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
王垣
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
尹善宇
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
<span class="item-key">配音</span>
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%82%93%E8%82%87%E5%9F%BA">邓肇基</a>
</span>
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
九王子，自认具备王储资质，但并无人认可他的才能。关注外貌且奢侈，挥金如土，身边常有人簇拥，但并无真心之交。看似对世上发生的事了如指掌，实则缺乏深刻的了解分析，如墙头草般，哪边有利往哪边倒。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item more">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%83%8A%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BD/19226575/0/4ec2d5628535e5ddca8ac35f7ec6a7efcf1b628f?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/-vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D0%2C0%2C652%2C927%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=af99091fac0f4bfb989fc4143e7f54c0/4ec2d5628535e5ddca8ac35f7ec6a7efcf1b628f.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
虞姬
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BE%90%E7%8F%A0%E8%B4%A4">徐珠贤</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
<span class="item-key">配音</span>
<span class="item-value">
杨婉潼
</span>
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
后百济的最后一位公主，隐藏自己的真实身份生活，在仙女般的舞姿伪装下，为了达到目的成为歌妓，是外表和内心有着反差的人物。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item more">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%83%8A%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BD/19226575/0/342ac65c10385343fcf7e1a19b13b07eca808871?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D0%2C0%2C652%2C927%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=cff9907ecbfdfc03f137b9f8e90faba4/342ac65c10385343fcf7e1a19b13b07eca808871.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%9A%87%E7%94%AB%E8%8E%B2%E8%8A%B1">皇甫莲花</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%A7%9C%E6%B1%89%E5%A8%9C">姜汉娜</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
<span class="item-key">配音</span>
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%99%B6%E6%95%8F%E5%A8%B4">陶敏娴</a>
；郑家蕙
</span>
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
公主，太祖王建和神静王后皇甫氏所生之女，美丽又霸气，八王子王旭的妹妹，后来嫁给了王昭，并最终成为王后。凭借其利落的性格和天生的政治才能，成为了亲手将目标扶上皇位并以此保护家门的造王者。她对丈夫王昭一片真心，奈何王昭心中只有解树，委屈不甘的她也只能黯然伤神。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item more">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%83%8A%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BD/19226575/0/4610b912c8fcc3ceacafafb39a45d688d53f20c6?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D0%2C0%2C652%2C927%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=3e6f752751ee3d6d3689dd8b7e264112/4610b912c8fcc3ceacafafb39a45d688d53f20c6.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
朴顺德
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%B1%A0%E8%B5%AB%E6%8B%89/18151987" data-lemmaid="18151987">池赫拉</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
<span class="item-key">配音</span>
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%BB%84%E7%BB%AE%E5%A9%B7">黄绮婷</a>
</span>
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
大将军朴守卿之女、十王子王银的夫人，从小跟随父亲辗转战场习武，巾帼不让须眉。不顾父亲的反对强行与王银成婚，但对方一心挂念解树，令她黯然神伤。聪慧渊博的她，只要面对十王子就紧张发抖说不出话，被众人笑称“傻瓜”，对十王子的一片痴心永远不变。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item more">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%83%8A%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%BD/19226575/0/0823dd54564e9258985ce06e9482d158cdbf4ec1?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D0%2C0%2C652%2C927%3Bh%3D195%3Bq%3D95/sign=b14cd5a83e7adab4299f4103b6e49f2c/0823dd54564e9258985ce06e9482d158cdbf4ec1.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
彩玲
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%A7%A6%E5%9F%BA%E5%91%A8">秦基周</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
<span class="item-key">配音</span>
<span class="item-value">
杨婉潼
</span>
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
解树的丫鬟，童年不幸，但有明朗的微笑和性格。为了养活家人而为奴，是不但不恨家人，反而为家人忧心的善良的女子。与解树亲密无间，后期得知一个连解树都不知道的特大秘密。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
