<a name="6" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub19650730_6" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="幕后花絮" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">步步惊心：丽</span>幕后花絮</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="6" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<ol class="custom_num  para-list list-paddingleft-1"><li class="list-num-1-1 list-num-paddingleft-1"><div class="para" label-module="para">该剧是<a target=_blank href="/item/NBC%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83">NBC环球</a>投资的第一部亚洲电视剧，采用100%先拍后播的模式制作。</div>
</li><li class="list-num-1-2 list-num-paddingleft-1"><div class="para" label-module="para">该剧举行开机仪式时，虽然现场没有烧猪，但整个过程简单而隆重，出席的演员及幕后工作人员均要趴在地上诚心跪拜，祈求剧集有高收视<sup>[21]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[21]_19650730">&nbsp;</a>
。</div>
</li></ol><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="7" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
